  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Student Care Area Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee the smooth operation of multiple student care centres within the designated area.</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain strong relationships with key stakeholders, including school management, parents, and internal/external partners.</li>\n  <li>Lead, mentor, and support a team of Supervisors and Programme Staff.</li>\n  <li>Provide regular training and motivation to enhance staff performance and engagement.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and improve classroom management practices across centres.</li>\n  <li>Provide guidance and counselling to students and staff facing behavioural or disciplinary challenges.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and submit weekly and monthly operational reports to management.</li>\n  <li>Plan, organise, and oversee the execution of annual events and centre activities.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma qualification.</li>\n  <li>Completion of relevant Student Care-related certifications.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of working experience in a related field.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Proven ability in leadership and team management.</li>\n  <li>Skills and traits required: Leadership, Management, Teamwork, Classroom Management, Counselling, Dedication, Detail-Oriented, Passionate, and Committed.</li>\n</ul>",
